WEBVTT

00:00:00.618 --> 00:00:02.056
When I was born,

00:00:02.056 --> 00:00:03.736
there was really only one book

00:00:03.736 --> 00:00:05.622
about how to raise your children,

00:00:05.622 --> 00:00:08.789
and it was written by Dr. Spock.

00:00:08.789 --> 00:00:10.725
(Laughter)

00:00:10.725 --> 00:00:11.956
Thank you for indulging me.

00:00:11.956 --> 00:00:15.562
I have always wanted to do that.

00:00:15.562 --> 00:00:17.665
No, it was Benjamin Spock,

00:00:17.665 --> 00:00:21.515
and his book was called "The Common
Sense Book of Baby And Child Care."

00:00:21.515 --> 00:00:27.162
It sold almost 50 million copies 
by the time he died.

